cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with 3D reconstruction and object detection using RGB-D scans, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also introduces a new data-driven approach using neural networks, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of their approach for virtual and robotic agents, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR).
